			<div class="col-md-11 col-sm-11 col-xs-12 no-padding">
				<h1>Shorteners/Redirectors: short of ideas</h1>
<div class="excerpt">We&#8217;ve been having some discussion internally about shortened URLs, with specific reference to pointing to web resources on Twitter, where you can&#8217;t actually avoid using shortened URLs, because an uncompressed URL is automatically shortened using bit.ly. You may remember that I discussed these issues before here, The main problem, of course, is that it&#8217;s all too</div>
